vernac_cmds: Class Adjointness (L: Language) {minL: MinimunLanguage L} (Gamma: ProofTheory L) (prodp funcp: expr -> expr -> expr): Prop := { adjoint: forall x y z, |-- prodp x y --> z <-> |-- x --> (funcp y z) }.
Class Commutativity (L: Language) {minL: MinimunLanguage L} (Gamma: ProofTheory L) (prodp: expr -> expr -> expr): Prop := { prodp_comm_impp: forall x y, |-- prodp x y --> prodp y x }.

Class Monotonicity (L: Language) {minL: MinimunLanguage L} (Gamma: ProofTheory L) (prodp: expr -> expr -> expr): Prop := { prodp_mono: forall x1 y1 x2 y2, |-- x1 --> x2 -> |-- y1 --> y2 -> |-- prodp x1 y1 --> prodp x2 y2 }.

Class Associativity (L: Language) {minL: MinimunLanguage L} (Gamma: ProofTheory L) (prodp: expr -> expr -> expr): Prop := { prodp_assoc1: forall x y z, |-- prodp x (prodp y z) --> prodp (prodp x y) z; prodp_assoc2: forall x y z, |-- prodp (prodp x y) z --> prodp x (prodp y z) }.

Class LeftUnit (L: Language) {minL: MinimunLanguage L} (Gamma: ProofTheory L) (e: expr) (prodp: expr -> expr -> expr): Prop := { left_unit1: forall x, |-- prodp e x --> x; left_unit2: forall x, |-- x --> prodp e x }.

Class RightUnit (L: Language) {minL: MinimunLanguage L} (Gamma: ProofTheory L) (e: expr) (prodp: expr -> expr -> expr): Prop := { right_unit1: forall x, |-- prodp x e --> x; right_unit2: forall x, |-- x --> prodp x e }.
Context {L: Language} {minL: MinimunLanguage L} {Gamma: ProofTheory L} {minAX: MinimunAxiomatization L Gamma} {prodp funcp: expr -> expr -> expr} {Adj: Adjointness L Gamma prodp funcp}.
Lemma prodp_mono1: forall x1 x2 y, |-- x1 --> x2 -> |-- prodp x1 y --> prodp x2 y.
Lemma funcp_mono2: forall x y1 y2, |-- y1 --> y2 -> |-- funcp x y1 --> funcp x y2.
Lemma adjoint_modus_ponens: forall x y, |-- prodp (funcp x y) x --> y.
Lemma adjoint_iter: forall x xs y, |-- fold_left prodp xs x --> y <-> |-- x --> (fold_right funcp y xs).
revert x; induction xs; intros; simpl in *.
Lemma Adjoint2Mono: Monotonicity L Gamma prodp.
Lemma funcp_mono: forall x1 y1 x2 y2, |-- x2 --> x1 -> |-- y1 --> y2 -> |-- funcp x1 y1 --> funcp x2 y2.
Context {L: Language} {minL: MinimunLanguage L} {Gamma: ProofTheory L} {minAX: MinimunAxiomatization L Gamma} {prodp: expr -> expr -> expr} {Mono: Monotonicity L Gamma prodp}.
Lemma fold_left_mono: forall x1 x2 xs1 xs2, (Forall2 (fun x1 x2 => |-- x1 --> x2) xs1 xs2) -> |-- x1 --> x2 -> |-- fold_left prodp xs1 x1 --> fold_left prodp xs2 x2.
Lemma fold_right_mono: forall x1 x2 xs1 xs2, (Forall2 (fun x1 x2 => |-- x1 --> x2) xs1 xs2) -> |-- x1 --> x2 -> |-- fold_right prodp x1 xs1 --> fold_right prodp x2 xs2.
Lemma fold_left_mono2: forall x1 x2 xs, |-- x1 --> x2 -> |-- fold_left prodp xs x1 --> fold_left prodp xs x2.
Lemma fold_right_mono2: forall x1 x2 xs, |-- x1 --> x2 -> |-- fold_right prodp x1 xs --> fold_right prodp x2 xs.

Context {L: Language} {minL: MinimunLanguage L} {Gamma: ProofTheory L} {minAX: MinimunAxiomatization L Gamma} {prodp: expr -> expr -> expr} {e: expr} {Mono: Monotonicity L Gamma prodp} {Assoc: Associativity L Gamma prodp} {LU: LeftUnit L Gamma e prodp} {RU: RightUnit L Gamma e prodp}.
Lemma assoc_fold_left_cons: forall x xs, |-- fold_left prodp xs (prodp e x) --> prodp x (fold_right prodp e xs).
Lemma assoc_fold_right_cons: forall x xs, |-- prodp x (fold_right prodp e xs) --> fold_left prodp xs (prodp e x).
Lemma assoc_fold_left_fold_right: forall xs, |-- fold_left prodp xs e --> fold_right prodp e xs.
Lemma assoc_fold_right_fold_left: forall xs, |-- fold_right prodp e xs --> fold_left prodp xs e.
Lemma assoc_prodp_fold_left: forall xs1 xs2, |-- prodp (fold_left prodp xs1 e) (fold_left prodp xs2 e) --> fold_left prodp (xs1 ++ xs2) e.
Lemma assoc_fold_left_app: forall xs1 xs2, |-- fold_left prodp (xs1 ++ xs2) e --> prodp (fold_left prodp xs1 e) (fold_left prodp xs2 e).
eapply aux_minimun_rule02; [| apply prodp_mono; apply assoc_fold_right_fold_left].
